{"tid":1676762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心大風向 不同網址的內容農場，背後疑由同一集團操作","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T02:45:33.000Z","uid":33373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e4679646387d5a89e76fe8aed1d7cb9bbc5370","tid":1676762,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"最近似乎出現一批新興的內容農場，專門刊載跟香港示威相關的新聞、「連登」LIHKG討論區上的熱門帖文等，相信均未經授權。<br />\n從流量角度考慮，6月至今的示威抗爭備受香港人關注，內容農場轉載相關文章、新聞屬意料之內。此外，自8月31日警察闖進太子站打人更趕走記者後，坊間越來越多未經證實傳聞甚至陰謀論，主要原因是政府及警隊的公信力跌至新低，有民調顯示超過一半受訪者完全不信任警方[1]，這也是有利內容農場擴張的環境，可以預期這類內容農場短期內不會消失。<br />\n有見及此，我收集了一批內容農場網站，簡單整理一下及嘗試找出其潛在關聯，結論是這些網站背後很可能是同一集團操作。<br />\n<br />\n利用「跳板」轉換網址<br />\n<br />\n分析涉及的網址共有36個，主要在Facebook上找到，有些是朋友分享，有些是在涉嫌由內容農場打理的專頁上看到，但並非有系統搜尋，肯定有更多漏網之魚。（完整資料見文末連結。）這36個網站可分為兩種︰跳板網站及內容農場&mdash;&mdash;「跳板網站」像縮短網址服務，點進去後會前往真正刊載內容的內容農場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情入去睇 用手機 好難轉貼啲文上黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F126592&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=e3ddaf11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592</a>"},{"pid":"5cc7ef5d810b3cb85615b413ca2ccf8b1c266e87","tid":1676762,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHGi4MT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHGi4MT.gif&h=925206fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ff4c5ee910031ae966d3c50f63a6cc60c50f4f5","tid":1676762,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa0fd557c9a5f55d1181d0d46cd03394928858","tid":1676762,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n共產黨用fake news反擊了"},{"pid":"0674db05ae0dfd8ea11d6f08ad93018ff8a4e0a6","tid":1676762,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fee7fc13290e662f0b76ce2c291b33bc656a34","tid":1676762,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce969dc5dc4ab9a0c0f96816ac9216d07ad8b75a","tid":1676762,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}